Robert E. CREWS v. COMMISSIONER OF INTERNAL REVENUE. No. 1170. Circuit Court of Appeals, Tenth Circuit. Nov. 28, 1934. Albert L. McRill, of Oklahoma City, Okl., for petitioner. *997Robert H. Jackson, Asst. Gen. Counsel, Bureau of Internal Revenue, of 'Washington, D. C., for respondent.

Before LEWIS and PHILLIPS, Circuit J udges.

PER CURIAM.

Petition for review dismissed on motion of respondent, petitioner consenting.
